Product




Chahil.com is home base to Satjiv Chahil's advising firm. Satjiv is one of Silicon Valley's most decorated marketers, having spent time as CMO of Palm, stood on stage with Steve Jobs as SVP at Apple, brought the HP brand back to life with iconic campaigns, as well as brought Beats by Dre headset to market. After retiring from the technology industry, Satjiv's reemergence was met… · More with enthusiasm from Silicon Valley. Right out of the gates Satjiv contributed to the marketing efforts of companies at startup stage to major brands such as Mercedes-Benz, Swarovski, BMW, and Sony. 






