VERA-JI  Trademark Information
 Satjiv S. Chahil
Advent calendars; Calendar desk pads; Calendar desk stands; Calendar refills; Calendar stands; Calendar-finished paper; Calendars; Calendars and diaries; Desk calendars; Note cards that unfold to act as worksheets for daily/monthly planners, organizers, calendars, to do lists that re-fold to make a credit card sized item that fits neatly in your wallet or pocket; Organizational kits containing calendars, stationery, planning folders, templates...




