 Mark Description: 
The mark consists of text that reads "VERA-JI" in a red cursive font. The font begins in the lower left corner and inclines towards the top right. It is placed in the middle of a square with a white background. The descending piece of the letter "J" extends under "VERA". All characters are capitalized, except for the letter "I" at the end. The dot of the "I" character is a copyright "C" in a circle.


